snippet.title: Jajikaya Jajikaya Lyrical Video - Akhanda 2 Thaandavam | NBK | Boyapati Srinu | Samyuktha |Thaman S
snippet.description:
Watch & Enjoy Jajikaya Jajikaya Lyrical Video from the Movie Akhanda 2 Thaandavam.

God Of Masses NBK, Blockbuster Maker Boyapati Sreenu, Raam Achanta, Gopi Achanta, 14 Reels Plus, M Tejaswini N Presents #BB4 Titled Akhanda 2.

Akhanda 2 Thaandavam In Theaters 5th Dec 2025

Song Details:-

Song Name: Jajikaaya
Music: Thaman S
Lyrics: Kasarala Shyam 
Singers: Brijesh Shandilya, Shreya Ghoshal

Song Programmed & Arranged by: Thaman S
Beat & EDM Works: Beyond Sound (T)
Live percussions - Thaman S, Anandan Sivamani, The Gongura Band 
Additional Live Percussions: Krishna Kishore
Guitars & Mandolin: Subhani
Flute: Shashank 
Additional Programming: Shashank Alamuru, Osho V, Hari S R

Harmony Vocals : 
Vagdevi, Sruthi Ranjani, Adviteeya, Pranati, Sindhuja Srinivasan, Sahiti Chaganti, Pratyusha, Sruthika, Vaishnavi, Soujanya, Prakruthi, Akshaya, Nadapriya, Lakshmi Meghana, Sindhuja Tanuku, Swetha, Sunayana, Savitha, Sankeerthna, Malathi, Gayatri,Kalyani, Keerthi, Likhila

Vocal Supervision: Sri Krishna, Adviteeya

Recorded at V Studios ( Chn ) by Osho V & Hari @ Vibe ( HYD ), Rakesh @ Prasad (Hyd), Aswin (Reengara) 

Mix and Mastered by Shadab Rayeen @ New Edge ( Mumbai )
Assistant Engineers - Jazbaat, Sohamm, Prasad

Studio Assistance - Raju, Ranjith, Kannan, Lingam, & Pawan

snippet.title: DHURANDHAR Trailer Reaction! | Ranveer Singh | Sanjay Dutt | Akshaye Khanna
snippet.description:
Achara, Brandon and Vivan dive into the explosive trailer of Dhurander, a powerhouse Pan-India action spectacle set to redefine mass cinema! Directed with fierce vision and packed with electrifying screen presence, Dhurander brings together an unstoppable blend of high-octane action, gripping drama, and larger-than-life storytelling.

Set against the backdrop of political power, legacy, and rebellion, Dhurander follows a fearless hero rising against corruption, injustice, and a system designed to break him. With thunderous dialogue, intense character moments, and jaw-dropping set pieces, this trailer delivers every bit of the adrenaline fans were waiting for.

       (With immense sorrow in our hearts, we bring to you Heart-throb Yatra, in association with Studio Chant Audio Vision and NK Production.
This is our humble tribute to Zubeen Garg, the voice we grew up with, the music that healed us, the artist who became our own.
More than 100 artistes and the entire musical/technical fraternity of Assam have joined hands in this special journey to honour his unforgettable contribution to our music, our culture, and our lives.)
Heart-throb Yatra is our way of saying thank you...for the songs that made us smile, for the lyrics that gave us strength and for being the heartbeat of Assam.



Script & Directed : Lakhiranjan Dutta 
Video Director & Edited by : Apuraj Gogoi 
DOP: Apuraj Gogoi & Santush Changmai
Assist : Biki Sonowal


Music-Re arranged by :- Lakhiranjan, Prasannajyoti, Bhassker Saikia (Ritu) Mumbai, Bhaskar Neelom, AAarxslan, Himangsu Buragohain


Musicians:-  Lakhiranjan, Bhaskar Neelom, Santu Kakoti, Dr Krishna Narayan Dutta Baruah, Krishna  Narayan Baruah, Lovely Kashyap, Rocktim Sarma, Sandeep Sengupta, Debojit(Maina) Gogoi,Ashim Dowerah, Nilutpal Borgohain, Rajiv, Rohan, Joydev, Manash protim Konwar, Ayanjyoti Gogoi...

Studios : Studio CHANTaudio (Lakhiranjan) , RNB Recording Studio (Mumbai by Bhasshker)
Sound Recordist: Niya Neri) Temptation(Anupam) ,Studio Strings (Bhaskar Neelom)
Mixed and Mastering : Lakhiranjan , Bhaskor Neelom , Bhashker Saikia (Ritu Mumbai) Aarxslan , Himangshu Burahgohain , Prashannajyouti 


Singer:- Anupam Saikia, Torali Sarma, Bipin Chawdang, Bornali kalita, Madhab Ranjan, Dikshu Sharma, Rakesh Reeyan, Vreegu Kashyap, Lakhi Ranjan,Kushal Hazarika, Bhassker Saikia, Neena Saikia, Hirakjyoti Deka,Dr Krishna Narayan Dutta Baruah, Kalyani Dutta, Madhab Ranjan,  Padmarag Knowar, Pompi Purabi Medhi, Nilav Nita , Joydev Sonowal, Urbashi Kakoti Dutta, Prasannajyoti, Bornill Bibek, Priyanka Devi, Prity Rani Borgohain, Monsoon, Kanchan Dutta,Sanjib Saikia,    Tharmina Saikia, Chayanika Bori, Zinty Panging, Maina Himadri, Lakhya Munda, V.M Munda, Shrestha Kachari, Jyotisma Chetia, Sherya Chaudhry, Kerttana Dutta, Kritishna Prasad, Raju Bahadur chettry, Indirani Dutta Rajkhowa, Papori Sharma Dutta, Kabita Hazarika, Suraj Dutta, Manashjyoti Saikia, Niku Saikia, Radha Das, Aadwitta Saikia, Abhilasha Hazarika, Smritirekha Bordoloi,Reshmirekha Bordoloi Kakoti, Hrishikesh Saikia, Tarun Deori, Bidyut Deka, Jina Saikia, Priti Chowdhury, Tusha Das, Anurupa Kakoti, Krishna porishmita, Debashree Sarma, Kuhi Chetia, Pallabi Talukdar, Priyadarshani Kakoti, Deepa Chetia Dutta, Abhilasha Hazarika, Himakshi Konwar, Juri Das, Kangana Maina Kashyap, Gayatri Gogoi, Banchana Rajkumari.

Child Singer :- Jishyant Dutta (Banhi), Udipta suraj Dutta, Akayansha suraj Dutta,   Dibyanshu Dutta(Puhor),Himakhi Konwar, Hanvika Baruah, , Aanayana Bania, Leon Dowerah, Ram Boar.
                   
                      Special Thanks 
 Padma Das, Hiren Gohain, Rajen Gohain, Suresh Hatimuriya, Bhabesh Guswami, Lohit Gogoi, Deepak Gogoi, Bokul Das , Hridayananda Knowar, Sujit Bordoloi, Raju Bahadur Chettri, Biren Hazarika( Mahal), Ratan Chaudhry, Dony Hazarika, Dinesh Sonowal, Lakhi Narayan Gogoi, Bhavan Sonowal, Bidyut Deka, Montu Das,Pranabjyoti Baruah, Mrinal Mon, Jiten Das, Bhuban Gogoi, Rohit Sonar, Prandeep Hazarika, Sannidhya Bhuyan, Zessim Ahmed, Dinesh Das, Hiranya kaushik , Ankur , Madhurjya , Diganta , Dibakar , All stuff of & Chiphong ethenic Family , Bivash Borman ( First Impression ) Unique Creation , Debanga Raj , Akashdeep Deka Raju Bahadur Chetri , Akhim jyoti, Prasanna Bora (Vini).

       (With immense sorrow in our hearts, we bring to you Heart-throb Yatra, in association with Studio Chant Audio Vision and NK Production.
This is our humble tribute to Zubeen Garg, the voice we grew up with, the music that healed us, the artist who became our own.
More than 100 artistes and the entire musical/technical fraternity of Assam have joined hands in this special journey to honour his unforgettable contribution to our music, our culture, and our lives.)
Heart-throb Yatra is our way of saying thank you...for the songs that made us smile, for the lyrics that gave us strength and for being the heartbeat of Assam.
